{CorporationName}
                                         (the "Corporation")

 Policy Name:                  {PolicyName}

 Policy Number:                {PolicyNumber}

 Effective Date:               {PolicyEffectiveDate}

 Two signatures will be required on all cheques and banking documents (note: make this provision
 confirm with your Corporation's Bylaws). All invoices are reviewed by two signing officers prior
 to payment. The Board Chair (or Treasurer) must approve all non-budgeted invoices over $1,000.
 The Secretary plus one other signing officer signs all legal documents (note: make this provision
 confirm with your Corporation's Bylaws) once the Board approves these documents. The
 Executive Director/CEO plus one other signing officer signs all fund agreement/deed of gifts. All
 fund agreement/deed of gifts are approved by the Board. The Executive Director/CEO or
 Treasurer signs donation receipts.

 Monitoring:                   This policy will be reviewed on or around {ReviewDate}.

 Board Acceptance:             This policy was approved by resolution of the board of directors
                               of the Corporation on {EffectiveDate}, as confirmed by
